3
00:00:56,460 --> 00:00:58,430
Dasar gelandangan.

4
00:00:58,830 --> 00:00:59,860
Awas!

5
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,360
Menjijikan!

6
00:01:02,470 --> 00:01:03,870
Apa dia mati?

7
00:01:03,970 --> 00:01:06,100
Orang-orang Amerika akan
segera datang kapan saja.

8
00:01:06,210 --> 00:01:09,140
Sungguh memalukan,
di sini banyak gelandangan!

9
00:01:18,350 --> 00:01:20,320
Ibu...!

10
00:01:21,690 --> 00:01:25,150
Hari apa ini?

11
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:38,170
Setsuko...

12
00:01:47,820 --> 00:01:50,110
Satu lagi.

13
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:05,060
Benda apa ini?

14
00:02:05,170 --> 00:02:08,140
Buang saja!

15
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:22,850
Yang ini juga sudah mati.

16
00:02:22,950 --> 00:02:25,920
Kamu bisa tahu dari matanya.

